2026-04-04T06:12:01.717Z [info]: [0mGET /faq-list.html?cat=guide&data=%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20User%20Guide%22%2C%22desc%22%3A%22Everything%20you%20need%20to%20know%20to%20get%20started%22%2C%22questions%22%3A%5B%7B%22q%22%3A%22How%20do%20I%20get%20started%20with%20FOOTRADAPRO%3F%22%2C%22a%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%2012px%3B%5C%22%3EThe%20onboarding%20process%20is%20simple%20and%20efficient%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20complete%20the%20experience%20in%20a%20very%20short%20time%3A%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%208px%3B%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3E1.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20platform%20adopts%20a%20sandbox%20mechanism.%20After%20registration%2C%20new%20users%20receive%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3E10%2C000%20USDT%20test%20funds%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20experience%20the%20system%27s%20features%20risk-free.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%208px%3B%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3E2.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Enter%20the%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%5C%22%3EMatch%20Market%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20select%20a%20match%20that%20aligns%20with%20your%20strategy%20preferences.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%208px%3B%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3E3.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Submit%20a%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%5C%22%3Eone-click%20authorization%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20complete%20the%20strategy%20locking%20and%20execution%20configuration.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-top%3A%2012px%3B%5C%22%3EThe%20entire%20process%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20highly%20streamlined%20and%20can%20typically%20be%20completed%20within%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3E2%20minutes%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20helping%20new%20users%20quickly%20get%20started%20and%20experience%20the%20complete%20intelligent%20operation%20cycle.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%7D%2C%7B%22q%22%3A%22How%20does%20the%2010%2C000%20USDT%20test%20fund%20work%3F%22%2C%22a%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%2012px%3B%5C%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3E10%2C000%20USDT%20test%20fund%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20provided%20exclusively%20for%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%5C%22%3Eevery%20user%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20experience%20our%20complete%20rule-locked%20authorization%20system%20with%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3Ezero%20risk%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%208px%3B%5C%22%3EYou%20can%20use%20it%20for%20your%20first%20authorization.%20After%20settlement%2C%20you%20can%20view%20detailed%20settlement%20results%20and%20a%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%5C%22%3Epost-match%20analysis%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20the%20system%27s%20decision-making%20process.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThis%20allows%20you%20to%20fully%20experience%20the%20exact%20same%20operational%20process%20as%20our%20partners.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%7D%2C%7B%22q%22%3A%22Is%20there%20a%20minimum%20deposit%20requirement%3F%22%2C%22a%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%2012px%3B%5C%22%3ENo%2C%20there%20is%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3Eno%20mandatory%20deposit%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20You%20can%20fully%20experience%20the%20platform%20for%20free%20using%20your%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%5C%22%3E10%2C000%20USDT%20test%20funds%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%2012px%3B%5C%22%3EIf%20you%20choose%20to%20make%20a%20deposit%2C%20the%20minimum%20amount%20is%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3E100%20USDT%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIf%20you%20do%20not%20have%20an%20exchange%20or%20cold%20wallet%20for%20depositing%2C%20please%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%5C%22%3Econtact%20our%20support%20team%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20send%20the%20message%20%5C%22I%20need%20to%20deposit%5C%22.%20A%20specialist%20will%20provide%20professional%20assistance.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%7D%5D%7D [32m200[0m 1.144 ms - -[0m 
