2026-04-04T06:49:12.492Z [info]: [0mGET /faq-list.html?cat=funds&data=%7B%22title%22%3A%22Funds%20%26%20Settlement%22%2C%22desc%22%3A%22Deposits%2C%20withdrawals%2C%20and%20settlement%22%2C%22questions%22%3A%5B%7B%22q%22%3A%22When%20is%20the%20settlement%20completed%20after%20a%20match%20ends%3F%22%2C%22a%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%2012px%3B%5C%22%3ESettlement%20is%20completed%20automatically%20within%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3E5%20minutes%3C%2Fspan%3E%20after%20the%20official%20final%20result%20of%20the%20match%20is%20confirmed.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%2012px%3B%5C%22%3EWe%20verify%20the%20result%20across%20three%20independent%20official%20data%20sources%20to%20ensure%20accuracy.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20settled%2C%20funds%20are%20immediately%20credited%20to%20your%20wallet%20balance.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%7D%2C%7B%22q%22%3A%22What%20are%20the%20withdrawal%20fees%20and%20processing%20time%3F%22%2C%22a%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%2012px%3B%5C%22%3EWe%20have%20fixed%20the%20withdrawal%20fee%20at%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3E1%20USDT%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%208px%3B%5C%22%3EWithdrawals%20are%20processed%20within%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3E2%20hours%3C%2Fspan%3E%3B%20for%20supported%20networks%2C%20most%20withdrawals%20are%20completed%20within%205-20%20minutes.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20is%20%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3Eno%20maximum%20withdrawal%20limit%3C%2Fspan%3E%20for%20any%20user.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%7D%2C%7B%22q%22%3A%22Is%20my%20funds%20secure%20on%20FOOTRADAPRO%3F%22%2C%22a%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%2012px%3B%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%5C%22font-weight%3A%20600%3B%20color%3A%20%23FF6B00%3B%5C%22%3EYes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20User%20funds%20are%20held%20in%20segregated%20cold%20wallets%2C%20completely%20separate%20from%20our%20operational%20funds.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%2012px%3B%5C%22%3EAll%20transactions%20are%20recorded%20on%20an%20immutable%20ledger%2C%20and%20we%20undergo%20quarterly%20third-party%20security%20audits.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20rule-locked%20system%20ensures%20that%20funds%20can%20only%20be%20moved%20according%20to%20your%20pre-agreed%20authorization%20rules%2C%20with%20no%20manual%20access%20possible.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%7D%5D%7D [32m200[0m 2.216 ms - -[0m 
