%20funds%20are%20held%20in%20segregated%20cold%20wallets%2C%20completely%20separate%20from%20our%20operational%20funds.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20style%3D%5C%22margin-bottom%3A%2012px%3B%5C%22%3EAll%20transactions%20are%20recorded%20on%20an%20immutable%20ledger%2C%20and%20we%20undergo%20quarterly%20third-party%20security%20audits.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20rule-locked%20system%20ensures%20that%20funds%20can%20only%20be%20moved%20according%20to%20your%20pre-agreed%20authorization%20rules%2C%20with%20no%20manual%20access%20possible.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%7D%5D%7D [32m200[0m 1.110 ms - -[0m 
